## Constraints

- Apply all four lenses — do not skip any.
- Be honest: inflated assessments produce worse graphs, not better ones.
- Constraint-force claims must trace to the classified_edges (step 1).
- Do not execute arbitrary Python code in Jinja2 expressions (sandboxed execution).
- Handle missing variables gracefully.

